00:14:51.114 --> 00:14:54.534
So you see this whole world of extracellular vesicles.

247
00:14:55.474 --> 00:14:59.394
Every day, there's a new size particle being discovered.

248
00:14:59.854 --> 00:15:03.134
The larger ones like to break off the surface,

249
00:15:03.914 --> 00:15:07.434
and so they have their own unique cargo being

