255
00:15:23.774 --> 00:15:27.314
released into the circulation. And

256
00:15:27.354 --> 00:15:31.324
finally, the smallest one, there's exomeres, and now there's

257
00:15:32.054 --> 00:15:34.474
another smaller group called supermeres,

258
00:15:35.294 --> 00:15:39.174
and we don't know exactly where their origin is, but we suspect

259
00:15:39.254 --> 00:15:42.054
that the mitochondria is involved in their

260
00:15:42.134 --> 00:15:43.274
biogenesis.

261
00:15:45.654 --> 00:15:49.054
So here's a diagram of an extracellular vesicle.

